    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-gradient-brand text-ivory\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center\">\n\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans\">Share Your Experience</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-heading font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-medium leading-tight mb-5\">\n      Had a great experience? We'd love to hear from you.\n    </h2>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-body text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4 font-sans\">\n      Your feedback helps other patients find the care they need and helps our team keep improving. We value every review and take your thoughts seriously.\n    </p>\n\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-body-2 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-sans\">\n      Whether it was a positive experience or something we can do better, we want to hear about it. Your honest feedback makes our practice stronger.\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\">\n\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n      <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-cta-component-cta inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans bg-primary\">\n        Request a Consultation\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>"
